OL,3,CRail Firm GWR fined #1m after death of
OL,4,Ctrain passenger
OL,6,FRail operator Great Western Railway
OL,7,F(GWR) has been fined #1 million after
OL,8,Fpleading guilty to breaches of health
OL,9,Fand safety law, after the death of a
OL,10,Fwoman on a train.
OL,12,FBethan Roper, 28, was killed by an
OL,13,Foverhanging tree branch when she stuck
OL,14,Fher head out of the window of a train
OL,15,Ftravelling at 75mph near Twerton in
OL,16,FBath on December 1st 2018.
OL,18,FMiss Roper, from Penarth in South
OL,19,FWales, was returning home from a day
OL,20,Fout in Bath, where she had been
OL,21,FChristmas shopping with friends.
