OL,4,Ctrain passenger
OL,6,FThe incident happened just a few
OL,7,Fminutes after the train left Bath,
OL,8,Fwhen her head was struck by an ash
OL,9,Ftree branch growing on land adjacent
OL,10,Fto the line.
OL,12,FA post-mortem examination found Miss
OL,13,FRoper had died from head injuries.
OL,15,FIn 2016, a rail passenger died in a
OL,16,Fsimilar incident near Balham, south
OL,17,FLondon. Following that accident, the
OL,18,FRail Accident Investigation Branch
OL,19,F(RAIB) issued safety recommendations
OL,20,Fin May 2017.
