OL,3,CRail Firm GWR fined #1m after death of
OL,4,Ctrain passenger
OL,6,FAn investigation from the Office of
OL,7,FRail and Road (ORR) found that
OL,8,Falthough GWR was aware of a number of
OL,9,Fprevious incidents, and had produced a
OL,10,Frisk assessment in September 2017, the
OL,11,Frecommendations were not implemented
OL,12,Fbefore the fatal accident in 2018.
OL,14,FRichard Hines, ORR's Chief Inspector
OL,15,Fof Railways, said:
