OL,4,Ctrain passenger
OL,6,F"Our thoughts remain with the family
OL,7,Fand friends of Bethan Roper. Her death
OL,8,Fwas a preventable tragedy that
OL,9,Fhighlights the need for train
OL,10,Foperators to proactively manage risks
OL,11,Fand act swiftly when safety
OL,12,Frecommendations are made to keep their
OL,13,Fpassengers safe.
