OL,3,CRail Firm GWR fined #1m after death of
OL,4,Ctrain passenger
OL,6,F"Our investigation found that GWR fell
OL,7,Fshort in its responsibilities, and
OL,8,Fthis prosecution reflects the serious
OL,9,Fconsequences of that failure. We
OL,10,Fwelcome the actions taken since by GWR
OL,11,Fand the wider industry to reduce the
OL,12,Frisks. Safety must always remain the
OL,13,Ffirst priority across Britain's
OL,14,Frailways."
OL,16,FAs well as the fine, GWR also ordered
OL,17,Fto pay #78,000 in costs.
